Text: Super! have you more from these swedish classics? i think there was a few more from this serie

This is esentially three short films, the kind of exclusive ones you would expect to come free with a magazine in certain parts of europe. None of these small viginette films are listed on iafd.com or egafd.com but "Kvinnolust" is listed on bgafd.com, almost certainly due to the fact that it involves two major british pornographic stars of the era.
